dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Shale Point and Blackwells Corner quadrangles, Kern County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Shale Point and Blackwells Corner map
Geology Shale Point and Blackwells Corner quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Shale Point, CA 1953, AMS 2055 III SW-Series V895; Blackwells Corner, CA 1953, photorevised 1982, DMA 2055 III SE-Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
